Feb 14 (Reuters) - Meilleure Health International Industry Group Ltd:
* WUHU MEILLEURE TO BUY 20% EQUITY INTEREST OF YUNNAN HANSU BIOTECHNOLOGY FOR RMB60 MILLION FROM HEMP INVESTMENT
* APPLICATION MADE TO STOCK EXCHANGE FOR RESUMPTION OF TRADING IN SHARES WITH EFFECT FROM 15 FEB Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
